HEADWORD: Playhouse
<hw>Play"house`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>plegh⟦umac⟧s</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A building used for
